data.description: Nestled in a tranquil corner of a cul-de-sac, this particular home boasts a spacious living room, a potential second living room or office, three cozy bedrooms and a covered patio. At the heart of this remarkable 1 story home lies a grand living room, this space serves as the perfect setting for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The primary bathroom has a custom walk-in shower and dual sinks for your commodity. The additional living space can be transformed into a cozy den, library, home office or play area. Its location, separate from the living room, ensures privacy and tranquility, making it ideal for relaxation. Schedule your tour for this ready move in home today!
